sequenceDiagram
    participant User as President Horne
    participant Overseer as Project Overseer
    participant Director as Director
    participant ARES as ARES Protocol
    participant Vault as Artifact Vault
    participant Memory as Memory Loom

    User->>Overseer: Gives mission
    Overseer->>Director: Routes task
    Director->>ARES: Consults protocol if useful
    ARES-->>Director: Returns workflow guidance
    Director->>Vault: Creates or updates artifact
    Director->>Memory: Logs decision or action
    Overseer-->>User: Reports result
